{"id": "art-73", "label": "Art. 73", "title": "Art. 73", "slug": "art-73", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 73 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Administratorii sunt solidar\nr&#259;spunz&#259;tori <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de societate\npentru:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)realitatea\nv&#259;rs&#259;mintelor efectuate de <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)<span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> real&#259; a dividendelor pl&#259;tite;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)<span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> registrelor cerute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>lege</i> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> corecta lor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;inere</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)exacta\nîndeplinire a hot&#259;rârilor adun&#259;rilor generale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)stricta\nîndeplinire a îndatoririlor pe care <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i>,\nactul constitutiv le impun.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_101844430\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2417\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_101844430\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În\ncazul în care societatea se afl&#259; în stare de dificultate,\nadministratorii/directorii au în vedere cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nurm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_115288741\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2416\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_115288741\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)interesele creditorilor, ale <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\nde titluri de <span class=SpellE>participa&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nale altor <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> interesate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2076721428\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2415\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2076721428\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)necesitatea de a lua m&#259;suri rezonabile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> adecvate pentru evitarea <span class=SpellE>insolven&#355;ei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pentru reducerea la minimum a pierderilor\nsuferite de creditori, de angajai, de <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torii</span>\nde titluri de <span class=SpellE>participa&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde alte <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> interesate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1293593987\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2414\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1293593987\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)necesitatea de a evita adoptarea, cu <span class=SpellE>inten&#355;ie</span>\nsau din grav&#259; <span class=SpellE>neglijen&#355;&#259;</span>, a unei\nconduite care <span class=SpellE>amenin&#355;&#259;</span> viabilitatea\nîntreprinderii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;iunea</span>\nîn r&#259;spundere împotriva administratorilor <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> creditorilor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ncare o vor putea exercita numai în caz de deschidere a procedurii reglementate\nde <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>64/1995</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nprocedura reorganiz&#259;rii judiciare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\nfalimentului, republicat&#259;.</span></p>"}